# ERI Project Structure

## Project Overview

This is an Employee Rights Protection System (ERI) with both frontend and backend components.

## Directory Structure

```
/
├── eoc_front/                    # Frontend React/Next.js application
│   └── src/
│       └── app/
│           └── (pages)/
│               └── consultation/
│                   └── expert/
│                       └── page.js    # Expert consultation page
│       └── shared/
│           └── layouts/
│               └── footer.js          # Footer component
│   └── public/
│       └── footer-bg.svg             # Footer background image
│
└── ERI/                          # Backend database and DDL files
    └── database/
        ├── ERI_DDL_PostgreSQL.sql           # Main DDL with 8 sections
        ├── ERI_EMPLOYEE_DDL_PostgreSQL.sql  # Employee management DDL
        ├── ERI_MG_DDL_PostgreSQL.sql        # Management system DDL
        ├── CONSULTATION_BOARD_DDL.sql       # Consultation board DDL
        ├── FILE_ATTACH_DDL.sql              # File attachment DDL
        ├── IMAGE_BOARD_DDL.sql              # Image board DDL
        └── SURVEY_RESPONSE_DDL.sql          # Survey system DDL
```

## Key Files

- [ERI/database/ERI_DDL_PostgreSQL.sql](mdc:ERI/database/ERI_DDL_PostgreSQL.sql): Main database schema with 8 sections including expert consultation
- [eoc_front/src/app/(pages)/consultation/expert/page.js](<mdc:eoc_front/src/app/(pages)/consultation/expert/page.js>): Expert consultation frontend
- [eoc_front/src/app/shared/layouts/footer.js](mdc:eoc_front/src/app/shared/layouts/footer.js): Footer component with SVG background

## System Components

1. **Self-Care System**: Employee wellness and self-management
2. **Habit Challenge**: Employee engagement and habit tracking
3. **Program Application**: Program registration and management
4. **Counseling Application**: General counseling services
5. **Shortcut Management**: Quick access features
6. **Common Code Management**: System-wide code tables
7. **Employee Rights Board**: Employee rights and complaints
8. **Expert Consultation**: Specialized consultation services

## Development Guidelines

- Follow established naming conventions for database objects
- Use Korean comments and descriptions
- Implement responsive design for frontend
- Maintain consistent code structure across all files
- Apply proper error handling and validation
